    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A dashboard-style SPA is chosen to transform the static strategic plan into an actionable tool. The structure includes: 1) An interactive event timeline to visualize the week's flow. 2) A powerful, filterable sponsorship hub where the user can dynamically sort targets by tier, market, and industry, directly aiding the search for optimal partners. 3) Summary charts to provide a quick, high-level overview of the sponsorship landscape. This user-centric, task-oriented design is more effective for an event coordinator than a linear document. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Report Info: Event Schedule -> Goal: Visualize week flow -> Viz: Interactive card-based timeline -> Interaction: Click/Hover -> Justification: Allows quick navigation and context. | Report Info: Sponsor Lists -> Goal: Organize & Find Optimal Partners -> Viz: Filterable Card Grid -> Interaction: Click filters -> Justification: Core functionality for the coordinator to narrow down targets. | Report Info: Sponsor Tiers/Types -> Goal: Summarize Strategy -> Viz: Donut & Bar Charts (Chart.js) -> Interaction: None -> Justification: Provides an at-a-glance understanding of the partnership mix and value. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->

